expression = re.compile(rfc._TIME_REGEX)
bad_times = ['a', "one o' clock", '9:52', '9:52am', '6:34:27', '19:4:27',
    '19:34:7', '12:34:27pm']
for bad_time in bad_times:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_time)), msg=
        "Bad Time '{t}' was not flagged".format(t=bad_time))
